OL,3,C'Absolute hell': Villagers on HS2 line
OL,4,Csay they're still living a nightmare
OL,6,FA homeowner in Water Orton tells ITV
OL,7,FNews Central reporter Pablo Taylor
OL,8,Fthat the "devastation and the
OL,9,Fdisruption and the total lack of
OL,10,Fconsideration by the HS2 workers" has
OL,11,Fmade their village "absolute hell"
OL,13,FResidents of a village in Warwickshire
OL,14,Fthat sits of the path of HS2's line
OL,15,Ffrom London to Birmingham say they are
OL,16,Fstill living a nightmare years after
OL,17,Fconstruction work began.
