OL,3,C'Absolute hell': Villagers on HS2 line
OL,4,Csay they're still living a nightmare
OL,6,FWork has been ongoing in Water Orton
OL,7,Fto build two giant viaducts that will
OL,8,Fcarry the high speed trains over the
OL,9,Fbusy M42 and M6 Toll motorways.
OL,11,FHS2 says they have been designed to
OL,12,Fblend seamlessly into their
OL,13,Fsurroundings.
OL,15,FBut Lynda Davies, a local resident,
OL,16,Fsays the work has turned what was a
OL,17,Fquiet, peaceful village into a
OL,18,Fbuilding site.
