OL,3,C'Absolute hell': Villagers on HS2 line
OL,4,Csay they're still living a nightmare
OL,6,F"It's been absolute hell. The
OL,7,Fdevastation and the disruption and the
OL,8,Ftotal lack of consideration by the HS2
OL,9,Fworkers and the traffic lights and the
OL,10,Fdust and the dirt and the pollution is
OL,11,Fjust unbelievable really. It really
OL,12,Fis."
OL,14,FHS2 says the viaducts in Water Orton
OL,15,Fwill be 20 metres in height at their
OL,16,Fhighest point.
