OL,3,C'Absolute hell': Villagers on HS2 line
OL,4,Csay they're still living a nightmare
OL,6,FThey will be held up by a series of 32
OL,7,Fgiant supporting columns and will hold
OL,8,F700 metres of new HS2 track over the
OL,9,FRiver Tame and a network of existing
OL,10,Ftransport links.
OL,12,FHS2 Ltd says it tries to minimise the
OL,13,Fimpacts of construction wherever
OL,14,Fpossible and encourages residents to
OL,15,Fkeep raising their concerns.
OL,17,FOne of those residents is Felicitas
OL,18,FFreeman who lives with a stone's throw
OL,19,Fof the viaduct site.
