OL,3,C'Absolute hell': Villagers on HS2 line
OL,4,Csay they're still living a nightmare
OL,6,FShe has been in constant contact with
OL,7,FHS2 about the flooding on her road,
OL,8,Fwhich she claims has worsened since
OL,9,Fconstruction began and reduced the
OL,10,Fvalue of her home.
OL,12,FShe said: "The estate agent didn't
OL,13,Freally want to come out to
OL,14,FAttenborough lane because he said it
OL,15,Fwas hard to value something that is
OL,16,Fblighted.
OL,18,F"It's a difficult situation.
OL,20,F"Property prices are suppressed here.
OL,21,FWho wants to live next door to HS2?"
