OL,3,C'Absolute hell': Villagers on HS2 line
OL,4,Csay they're still living a nightmare
OL,6,F"All the other community clubs in the
OL,7,Fvillage were getting something and I
OL,8,Fthought well we'll give it a go and we
OL,9,Fmanaged to get that and the club's
OL,10,Fgrown from there."
OL,12,FEarlier this week HS2 announced it had
OL,13,Freached a milestone in completing more
OL,14,Fthan half of the tunnels required for
OL,15,Fthe rail project.
OL,17,FConstruction is due to finish in the
OL,18,Fearly 2030s.
